            <div class="col-12 col-lg-9">
                <div class="image-wrapper"><div class="image_style" style="width:96%;"><picture><source sizes="(min-resolution: 4dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 4) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (min-resolution: 3dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 67vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 3) and (max-width: 700px) 65vw, (min-resolution: 2.5dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2.5) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (min-resolution: 2dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px" srcset="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:640/format:webp/1*58T-GM174aZdare7hacgyQ.png 640w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:720/format:webp/1*58T-GM174aZdare7hacgyQ.png 720w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:750/format:webp/1*58T-GM174aZdare7hacgyQ.png 750w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:786/format:webp/1*58T-GM174aZdare7hacgyQ.png 786w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:828/format:webp/1*58T-GM174aZdare7hacgyQ.png 828w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1100/format:webp/1*58T-GM174aZdare7hacgyQ.png 1100w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1400/format:webp/1*58T-GM174aZdare7hacgyQ.png 1400w" type="image/webp"/><source data-testid="og" sizes="(min-resolution: 4dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 4) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (min-resolution: 3dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 67vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 3) and (max-width: 700px) 65vw, (min-resolution: 2.5dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2.5) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (min-resolution: 2dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px" srcset="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:640/1*58T-GM174aZdare7hacgyQ.png 640w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:720/1*58T-GM174aZdare7hacgyQ.png 720w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:750/1*58T-GM174aZdare7hacgyQ.png 750w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:786/1*58T-GM174aZdare7hacgyQ.png 786w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:828/1*58T-GM174aZdare7hacgyQ.png 828w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1100/1*58T-GM174aZdare7hacgyQ.png 1100w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1400/1*58T-GM174aZdare7hacgyQ.png 1400w"/><img alt="" loading="lazy" role="presentation" src="https://miro.medium.com/max/700/1*58T-GM174aZdare7hacgyQ.png"></picture></div><br></div></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;"><span>T</span><strong>hree days after</strong> my dad died, I received a thoughtful note from a trust and safety manager at Airbnb, wishing my family condolences and offering the company’s support. “If it would be all right with you, may I call later this week to check in and see if there’s anything you need?”</p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">I was tempted to say yes, but after looking up her credentials, I noticed that her previous employer was a Northern California police department, where she worked as a detective. Was this a condolence call or was it the beginning of an investigation?</p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">Probably a little bit of both: corporations often reach out to accident victims early, before they’ve had a chance to lawyer up. The goal is to get them to make a first offer on their demands, knowing that victims tend to lowball the price put on wrongful death or injury. Then, a settlement follows, after an NDA is signed, along with an admission that the company was not at fault.</p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="image3 cid-tt612oXwA9" id="image3-5" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-12 col-lg-9">
                <div class="image-wrapper"><div class="image_style" style="width:96%;"><picture><source sizes="(min-resolution: 4dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 4) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (min-resolution: 3dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 67vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 3) and (max-width: 700px) 65vw, (min-resolution: 2.5dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2.5) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (min-resolution: 2dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px" srcset="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:640/format:webp/1*QfX6lCnMFKf2VEwl9zacag.jpeg 640w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:720/format:webp/1*QfX6lCnMFKf2VEwl9zacag.jpeg 720w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:750/format:webp/1*QfX6lCnMFKf2VEwl9zacag.jpeg 750w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:786/format:webp/1*QfX6lCnMFKf2VEwl9zacag.jpeg 786w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:828/format:webp/1*QfX6lCnMFKf2VEwl9zacag.jpeg 828w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1100/format:webp/1*QfX6lCnMFKf2VEwl9zacag.jpeg 1100w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1400/format:webp/1*QfX6lCnMFKf2VEwl9zacag.jpeg 1400w" type="image/webp"/><source data-testid="og" sizes="(min-resolution: 4dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 4) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (min-resolution: 3dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 67vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 3) and (max-width: 700px) 65vw, (min-resolution: 2.5dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2.5) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (min-resolution: 2dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px" srcset="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:640/1*QfX6lCnMFKf2VEwl9zacag.jpeg 640w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:720/1*QfX6lCnMFKf2VEwl9zacag.jpeg 720w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:750/1*QfX6lCnMFKf2VEwl9zacag.jpeg 750w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:786/1*QfX6lCnMFKf2VEwl9zacag.jpeg 786w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:828/1*QfX6lCnMFKf2VEwl9zacag.jpeg 828w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1100/1*QfX6lCnMFKf2VEwl9zacag.jpeg 1100w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1400/1*QfX6lCnMFKf2VEwl9zacag.jpeg 1400w"/><img alt="" loading="lazy" role="presentation" src="https://miro.medium.com/max/700/1*QfX6lCnMFKf2VEwl9zacag.jpeg"></picture></div><br></div></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">“A man died, and you’ll never hear about it,” my mom has continued to say in the aftermath of her husband’s untimely demise. The papering over of real lives has, in fact, been my main motivation to write this piece. My family remains free to speak about Airbnb’s role in the accident since we never pursued legal action against them. Our lawyer — my dad’s best friend since college — extracted a settlement from the hosts’ homeowners’ insurance policy, which, lucky for us, did not deny coverage for commercial activity.</p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">We seem to be the exception to the rule. Most home insurance policies make exclusions for any commercial activity taking place for residential policies. In January, Airbnb introduced a new product: secondary coverage for hosts who might find their claims denied if something goes haywire during a home-sharing stay. Peers followed suit, with a policy that extends across home-sharing platforms. Given Airbnb’s history of reactive, as opposed to proactive, solutions, I imagine hosts have already found themselves in that conundrum and with the exposure it entails.</p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="image3 cid-tt612oXwA9" id="image3-5" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
